quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  55,46,Ve limen hafe mekame rabbihi cennetani
  55,47,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,48,Zevata efnanin
  55,49,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,50,Fiyhima ´aynani tecriyani
  55,51,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezzibani
  55,52,Fiyhima min kulli fakihetin zevcani
  55,53,Febieyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,54,Muttekiiyne ala furuşim betainuha min istebrak ve cenel cenneteyni dan
  55,55,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,56,Fihinne kasıratut tarfi lem yatmishunne insun kablehum ve la can
  55,57,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,58,Ke ennehunnel yakıtı vel mercan
  55,59,Fe be eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,60,Hel cezaul ıhsani illel ihsan
  55,61,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,62,Ve min dunihima cennetan
  55,63,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,64,Mudhammetan
  55,65,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,66,Fihima aynani neddahatan
  55,67,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,68,Fihima fakihetuv ve nahluv ve rumman
  55,69,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,70,Fihinne hayratun hısan
  55,71,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,72,Hurum maksuratun fil hıyam
  55,73,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,74,Lem yatmishunne insun kablehum ve la can
  55,75,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,76,Muttekiiyne ala rafrafin hudriv ve abkariyyin hısan
  55,77,Fe bi eyyi alai rabbikuma tukezziban
  55,78,Tebarakesmu rabbike zil celali vel ikram